<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your 9ja Market Marketer Account is Verified!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .container {
        border: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #009933;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .referral-code {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border: 1px dashed #ccc;
      }
      .steps {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .steps h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #009933;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
        font-size: 0.8em;
        color: #888;
      }
      .benefits {
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .benefits ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>9ja Market</h1>
        <p>Congratulations! Your Marketer Account is Verified</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>

        <p>
          Great news! Your application to become a 9ja Market Marketer has been
          approved. You're now ready to start onboarding merchants and earning
          commissions.
        </p>

        <div class="referral-code">
          <p>Your Unique Referrer Code:</p>
          <p><%= referrerCode %></p>
        </div>

        <p>
          Merchants can also use your username
          <strong><%= username %></strong> when registering. Either your
          referrer code or username will connect you to merchants you refer.
        </p>

        <div class="steps">
          <h3>How to Get Started:</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <strong>Reach out to vendors</strong> in your locality and in
              markets around you
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Explain the benefits</strong> of joining 9ja Market:
              <div class="benefits">
                <ul>
                  <li>Expanded online presence and visibility</li>
                  <li>Access to a wider customer base</li>
                  <li>Easy-to-use platform for managing products</li>
                  <li>Convenient payment processing</li>
                  <li>Support for growing their business digitally</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Guide them through registration</strong> and ensure they
              include your referral code or username
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Earn commissions</strong> when merchants you refer
              purchase advertising packages
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <p>
          You'll earn <strong><%= (10 * 100).toFixed(0) %>%</strong> commission
          on all ad placements purchased by merchants you refer. Your earnings
          will be calculated automatically and can be viewed in your dashboard.
        </p>

        <p>
          We recommend starting with merchants you already know and gradually
          expanding your network. Our most successful marketers focus on
          explaining how 9ja Market helps merchants grow their businesses
          online.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to
          contact our support team.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for partnering with 9ja Market!</p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          The 9ja Market Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> 9ja Market. All rights
          reserved.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this
          email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
